00:55:35.480 --> 00:55:39.871
- I got a guy who can fix your RV.
- I'm in far too much physical agony.

949
00:55:39.960 --> 00:55:43.635
I'm sorry. But it'll be good for you
to get out and about.

950
00:55:43.720 --> 00:55:46.951
Perfect. I can take the girls
shopping in Coconut Grove.

951
00:55:47.040 --> 00:55:49.679
Little Jack is on
a specific napping schedule.

952
00:55:49.760 --> 00:55:52.638
- I'd better stay here.
- No. Go.

953
00:55:52.720 --> 00:55:56.554
Greg can watch him.
He has wonderful parental instincts.

954
00:55:56.640 --> 00:55:59.757
Greg deals with little kids
in the E.R. All the time.

955
00:55:59.840 --> 00:56:02.479
They don't call me
Barry Poppins for nothing.

956
00:56:02.560 --> 00:56:04.516
That's funny.

957
00:56:04.600 --> 00:56:06.795
Why would someone
call you Barry Poppins?

958
00:56:10.880 --> 00:56:12.916
They wouldn't.
